    {
      "text": "Which of the following statements is true regarding the minimum age requirements for employing children in factories as per the Factories Act?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "Guaranteed employment for under 14-year-olds from below-poverty-line families in factories.",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "No employment for under 18-year-olds in factories.",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "Under 14-year-olds can be employed only in non-hazardous factory roles.",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "15-18 year olds need a fitness certificate for factory work from a certified surgeon",
          "correct": true
        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "D. 15-18 year olds need a fitness certificate for factory work from a certified surgeon",
      "question_images": [],
      "explanation_images": [],
      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:806px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Factory Act</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Definition</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>An establishment employing 10 or more workers where power is used or 20 or more workers where power is not used.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Applicability</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Applies to all of India and covers all factories, including <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"231e76e11c1692777195bd586f5b59\">perennial</span> and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"201a6ea7721692777198c51d735506\">seasonal</span> factories.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Age Restrictions</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(Option A, B and D)</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Prohibits employment of children below 14 years of age</strong>.</li>\n<li>15-18 year olds need fitness certificate for factory work from a certified surgeon</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Hours of Work</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Work limited to <strong>48 hours/week or 9 hours/day; max 60 hours/week with overtime</strong>.</li>\n<li>Adolescents: max 4.5 hours/day.</li>\n<li>Women and adolescents: work hours 6 am to 7 pm.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Leave</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Grants 1 day of leave per 15 days of work for adolescents</li>\n<li>1 day per 30 days of work for adults.</li>\n<li>Permits accumulation of leaves up to 40 days for adolescents and 30 days for adults.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Health & Safety</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Mandates a minimum of 500 cubic <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"32656dc8ba1692777202fc49f9ed13\">feet</span> of space per worker.</li>\n<li>Requires 1 safety officer per 1000 workers.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Welfare</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Stipulates 1 welfare officer per 500 workers, 1 canteen per 250 workers, and 1 <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4751516864169277718500f84f5fb3\">cr\u00e8che</span> per 30 women workers.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
