        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "D. Number of people per water point should be 150",
      "question_images": [],
      "explanation_images": [],
      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:586px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Water supply</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Safe water supply with chlorination.</li>\n<li><strong>Residual <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3c268a141b1692777184336bc40100\">chlorine</span> levels should be >0.7 mg/L for 1 hour contact period</strong> <strong>(Option A).</strong></li>\n<li>0.5 mg <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3c268a141b1692777184336bc40100\">chlorine</span> tablets sufficient for 20 L water <strong>(Option B).</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Food and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1f7e7543bc16927772015cdb525c2b\">Vector</span> control</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Safe food should be ensured</li>\n<li>To protect from <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fa7058cd8e16927772017bed30d85d\">vector-borne</span> diseases, rodenticides like <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"39ecb6e07416927772029550b7e74a\">zinc</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c7ee01df1b169277719539ad796de7\">phosphide</span> must be sprayed.</li>\n<li>Indoor <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a459f313d9169277719789fdfb7ada\">residual</span> sprays must be used for mosquitoes and sandflies.</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Accommodation guidelines</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Per person shelter space: 3.4 square meters</li>\n<li>Number of people per water point: 250 (option D)</li>\n<li>Distance to water point: 150 meters</li>\n<li>Number of people per latrine: 20</li>\n<li>Distance to latrine: 30 meters</li>\n<li>Distance between water point and latrine: 100 mts <strong>(Option C)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
