    {
      "text": "Which of the following is not a key activity of disaster preparedness?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "Risk assessment to identify specific hazards",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "Securing financial and logistical resources for preparedness and response",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "Public education programs to raise awareness about disaster risks and responses",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "Enforcing disaster-resistant building codes",
          "correct": true
        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "D. Enforcing disaster-resistant building codes",
      "question_images": [],
      "explanation_images": [],
      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:667px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Disaster Preparedness</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Aims to reduce the impact of hazards through long-term development.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Activities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Risk assessment to identify specific hazards (Option A)</li>\n<li>Establishing standards and regulations for construction and land use</li>\n<li>Developing communication, information, and warning systems for timely alerts</li>\n<li>Organizing and coordinating response mechanisms, including:\n\t\t\t\t<ol>\n<li>Training and equipping emergency personnel</li>\n<li>Establishing <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0705e4cf081692777187f4d2b512aa\">evacuation</span> procedures</li>\n<li>Stockpiling essential supplies</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>Securing financial and logistical resources for preparedness and response <strong>(Option B)</strong></li>\n<li>Public education programs to raise awareness about disaster risks and responses <strong>(Option C)</strong></li>\n<li>Collaboration with news media for effective information dissemination during emergencies</li>\n<li>Conducting disaster <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e80d309d691692777198f2f0f93cca\">simulation</span> exercises to test and improve response mechanisms</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Integration of Mitigation Measures</strong></p>\n<p>Disaster mitigation in disaster preparedness aims to minimize hazard impacts through proactive development efforts, enhancing <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b11364e7ed169277719777251a2bfe\">resilience</span> and emergency management capabilities.</p>\n<p>Empowers local individuals as first responders.</p>\n<p>Effective when communities manage internal and external assistance programs.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Multi-Sectoral Approach</strong></p>\n<p>Involves collaboration among government agencies, NGOs, communities, and individuals.</p>\n<p>Ensures a comprehensive and coordinated response to <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a3b8e7d7ec1692777192646b2c8f69\">mitigate</span> disaster risks and enhance resilience.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
